topics.body:
A crocodile walks into a bar, heads straight for the old biker lady all dressed in leather, covered in tattoos and smoking a cigarette while downing shots of whiskey. 

The crocodile immediately eats her up in one bite as the crowd watches in horror.

After eating her the crocodile turns to the bartender and says, "damn that was salty, let me get a beer."

The bartender shakes his head and says, "no, we don't serve drug users here."

"Drug user?!" the crocodile shouts, "I'm not a drug user!"

"Oh yeah?" says the bartender, "well what about that bar bitch you ate?"
